{
  "stem": "21731.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Maryla kept me for a few days and found me a job as a shoemaker with a friend of hers who was also a doctor's wife.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Her-- her husband was also in the army, and she made boots out of felt.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were special Polish boots called [POLISH].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I had no idea of shoe making, but I learned it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But in the meantime, Jan was at the Mariani, and Marisha let me know that he had to be moved somehow, but she will arrange that.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because the Mariani didn't-- couldn't keep him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was, I think, also a bit of a different child of the others.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was stubborn, and not-- not easy, I suppose.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But he had a very hard life, and I can't blame him.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, there certainly were Jewish children, but there were a lot of not Jewish children, but Polish children.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the Marianas had enough on their, and since they were not very helpful, Maryla had to move Jan somewhere.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she found a place in the county for him at a Polish gentleman who was very anti-German, naturally.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when he heard there's a child of a Polish officer whose mother is missing, or perhaps, dead-- not that he knew that he is Jewish, but a lot of Poles were taken away and killed, or whatever, arrested, and nobody heard anything about them.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Auschwitz, and-- and Dachau, and Bergen-Belsen was full of Polish people also.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So anyway, he agreed to have Jan, and Marisha paid for that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Not much, but something.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, somewhere near Warsaw, in the country.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Jan didn't like being there, because this engineer wasn't a very nice man.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But he had to stay there, and I couldn't do anything about it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I had no other place for him.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
